Package: digitraffic
Title: R Client for the Finntraffic Digitraffic TMS (LAM) API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Theo", "Blauberg", 
    email = "theo.blauberg@outlook.com", 
    role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1780-0365"))
Description: Provides functions to access traffic measurement data from the
    Finnish Transport Infrastructure Agency's Digitraffic open API. Covers
    TMS (Traffic Measurement System, known as LAM in Finnish) stations
    including real-time sensor data, station metadata, sensor calibration
    constants, and historical raw vehicle-level observations. All data is
    returned as tidy tibbles ready for analysis.
